snippet.title: Grapat Open Ended Wooden Toys Unboxing
snippet.description:
Hope you enjoy getting a closer look at our wooden Grapat toys that our kids love so dearly. The kids loved unboxing these wonderful open ended wooden toys. The colours and quality are amazing! The kids love creating their own little worlds with all the unique pieces. 

About Grapat
~
Grapat is a Spanish, family-run business, who design and make beautiful wooden toys. Inspired by their daughter's imaginative play, Casiana and Jordi create open-ended toys that encourage children to freely play, experiment and discover. Grapat toys are made using local, sustainable wood found around their Catalonian home. Discover the world of Rainbow Nins, and sort, hide, and store treasures with wooden bowls.

~

Grapat Wooden Toys from The Bendy Beanstalk
https://thebendybeanstalk.com/collections/grapat?sort_by=created-descending

Ostheimer Wooden Animals from The Bendy Beanstalk
https://thebendybeanstalk.com/collections/ostheimer?sort_by=title-ascending

Grimm's from The Bendy Beanstalk
https://thebendybeanstalk.com/collections/grimms?page=2&sort_by=best-selling

Hugo Loves Tiki
https://thebendybeanstalk.com/collections/hugo-loves-tiki

Lots of the toys, puzzles, games, books, bedding, and even clothes can be found in our store: https://thebendybeanstalk.com

Don't hesitate to message us on instagram about any product! http://www.instagram.com/thebendybeanstalk

~

We are a young Australian couple raising our six beautiful children aged 7, 6, 5, 4, 4, 4! That's right.. with the surprise addition of our sweet baby triplets, we had six children in three years!
Life can be pretty hectic sometimes, but it's also A LOT of fun!

snippet.title: Unboxing NEW Scruff-A-Luv Toys
snippet.description:
UNBELIEVABLE STORIES OF LITTLE LIVE PETS! Find and rescue little cute critters, wash and groom, enjoy having adorable fluffy friends!



Funny little Scruff-A-Luv pets are taking over the world and kids' hearts all over the world! Are you one of us? Don't worry if you don't have one of these cuties yet! Specially for you we are unboxing four adorable little stuffed animals!

Each of them comes in a cute little box and there are so many mystery treasures inside! First, you'll see a little ball of fur that doesn't look like anything. The only feature worth meantioning in this little guys are his giant sad eyes! And maybe color, Scruff-A-Luvs come in the most pretty pastel colors like baby blue, light pink, lav ender and sunny yellow. Put this furball aside for now and look at the rest. There's a collar with a name tag for your pet, a beautiful hair brush (or is it a fur brush?), a hair clip and an adoption certificate. Excited yet?

There's also a detailed step-by-step instruction on how to make this scruffy guy into a soft pet friend for you. First, you want to wash it. We don't normally use shampoo or soap but it's totally ok to do so. Once wet your pet will start to take shape and you'll find out if you got a little bunny, a kitty or a doggy. Then you'll need to groom your pet and dry its fur. Slick Slime Sam loves grooming our pets so I usually trust him with this task. Then name your little live pet and put his name on a name tag, l put on an accessory and have fun together!

I found this little dirty ball of fur on the street. What is it and what do I do to rescue it?

4:49 - 💗UNPACKING PINK SCRUFF A LUV

Now I found an abandoned pet right in front of our door! Who would do such a thing?

9:08 - 💜OPENING PURPLE SCRUFFY PET TOY

We fell in love with Scruff A Luvs and bought an extra cute purple buddy!

14:46 - 💛UNBOXING LIMITED EDITION YELLOW SCRUFF A LOVE

Is that a blossom bunny among the lemons? We need to rescue it!

It works by infrared (IR) technology that detects any surface below it and makes it hover and rise up!  It has a foam body that lets it withstand falls, crashes, or bounce of walls!  Its flashing LED lights makes it really COOL to fly at night! Other than just your hand, you can also try more advanced tricks like using your legs, knees, arms or shoulders!  Use the catching stick to play catch with friends and toss it back and forth!    Similar to Vectron Wave or Air Hogs or Air Eagle UFO Flyers
- Easy-to-fly hand-controlled Flying Saucer, UFO, perfect for beginners, no need for remote control

- Foam body lets it withstand falls and crashes, or lets it bounce of walls!
- Flashing LED lights make it really cool to fly at night!

- Play catch with friends and toss it back and forth with the use of the catching stick!
- Comes with USB charging cable and built-in rechargeable lithium batteries, charge for 20 minutes, good for 3-7 minutes of flying time.
- Fly indoors or outdoors, but keep away from people's faces, eyes, animals, and fragile objects.
